assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Iwabuchi Corporation manufactures and sells electrical overhead wire hardware for electric power, communication, signals, broadcasting, and railway industries in Japan. It offers power transmission and distribution equipment parts; communication equipment; broadcast receiving and supporting equipment; synthetic resin electrical insulation materials; and other electrical connection equipment. The company also undertakes construction, civil engineering, electrical, telecommunication, designing, supervision, and facility contracting works. In addition, it provides distribution line, CATV/information communication, traffic lights and road signs, school physical education facility, and disaster prevention radio services. Further, the company offers seismic technology, contract testing, and renewable energy related services, as well as services for EV charging stations. Iwabuchi Corporation was founded in 1950 and is headquartered in Matsudo, Japan.
